Hunting Quiver.description:
Increases your damage against Beasts and Dragonkin by 20% and your critical strike chance against them by 10%.

Only 1 |cffffffffQuiver|r may be active at a time.

@ext:Shares a cooldown with other |cffffffffQuivers|r.:ext@

Light Quiver.description:
Increases melee and ranged haste by 10% and reduces the Focus costs of abilities by 15%.

Only 1 |cffffffffQuiver|r may be active at a time.

@ext:Shares a cooldown with other |cffffffffQuivers|r.:ext@

Poison Quiver.description:
Ranged abilities fire a poisoned arrow, dealing 30 Nature damage over 15 sec, stacks 3 times.

Only 1 |cffffffffQuiver|r may be active at a time. 

@ext:Shares a cooldown with other |cffffffffQuivers|r.:ext@

Searing Quiver.description:
Ranged abilities deal 15% additional direct Fire damage to your target and up to 3 nearby enemies. This damage can benefit from your |cffffffffBurning Toxin|r and other effects that increase Fire damage and is able to critically strike.

Only 1 |cffffffffQuiver|r may be active at a time.

@ext:Shares a cooldown with other |cffffffffQuivers|r.:ext@

Skirmisher's Quiver.description:
Increases your Physical damage and your critical damage by 10%.

Only 1 |cffffffffQuiver|r may be active at a time.

@ext:Shares a cooldown with other |cffffffffQuivers|r.:ext@

